- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with optimizing the performance of a complex system with multiple components. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is relevant as the paper deals with communication delays between geographically distributed nodes. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a machine learning-based approach to solve a complex optimization problem.
